      "text": [
        "2207 - وَ أَيُّمَا بَعِيرٍ حُجَّ عَلَيْهِ ثَلاَثَ سِنِينَ جُعِلَ مِنْ نَعَمِ اَلْجَنَّةِ ».\nوروي \" سبع سنين \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2207 - \"Any camel on which Hajj is performed for three years will be made among the livestock of Paradise.\"\nIt has also been narrated: \"Seven years.\""
        ]
      }
